	(text "* Battery soft-disconnect resistor. If un-populated, it does not\n  disconnect the battery per se, it just prevents the battery charger\n  from sensing the battery's presence and voltage, and therefore\n  prevents it from driving SDRV.\n* The board will still work with external/USB power, but won't charge.\n  Hopefully, if un-populated, it will remove any battery-powered\n  quiescent power consumption from the system, which could work as an\n  even lower-powered form of ship mode, once said mode is activated.\n  A new revision of this board will replace this resistor with a switch\n  if this idea works.\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 144.272 40.132 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 0.762 0.762)
				(color 72 72 72 1)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "e503f29b-bce6-4ad8-bf81-ae537abf2207")
	)
